name: Supertech Services
overview:
Our product index encompasses a wide range of Equipment, Torches, Automation systems, Temperature Indicators, Gas Cutting & Regulation Equipments, TIG Electrodes, Safety Products sourced from reputed foreign manufacturer and brands like Miller USA, Weldcraft & Bernard USA, Jetline Engineering USA, Tempil USA, Smith USA, Plansee Austria and Sinotec Germany respectively.

Management Team: Our team comprises the following professionals: Trained & Professional Service Engineers Warehousing and Packaging staff Sales and Marketing executives

Our Strengths: In order to maintain a distinct image in the market along with the trust of our clients, we have always ensured that all the products promoted and marketed by us are of high quality quotient and we have been well known for the same ever since our inception itself. Such factors have enabled us to fulfill the requirements of the clients based in various parts of the country.

Our Infrastructure: We have state-of-the-art infrastructural set up that is a perfect amalgamation of latest technology and adroit workforce. To facilitate smoother and efficient activities, we constantly update our services/ testing equipment, workshops, warehouses as per the latest technological trends.
